{"tid":284162,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「 有圖慎入 」究竟呢個傷口係點形成","createTime":"2017-06-14T16:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T16:15:32.000Z","uid":37822,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"362b1ee9d070ce91ed6b5c9ea4054034ab7aa386","tid":284162,"uid":37822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/003830_daff7801b91d54db0dfc6668f1e7e8cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F003830_daff7801b91d54db0dfc6668f1e7e8cb.jpg&h=64788cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你既巴打我就做廚房既 <br />\n一收工就感覺到隻手有啲乸乸地<br />\n就見到咁既傷口<br />\n我就唔知係漂水整到<br />\n定油炸到<br />\n我懷疑係共用手套整到 <br />\n大家點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c04e240669679404b4588b5e7e2aa9e83a72427","tid":284162,"uid":43480,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"太乾？"},{"pid":"b88cdad70d2ade3b3372762f73b2acc2e025b039","tid":284162,"uid":33031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:46:28.000Z","msg":"樓主一路好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7402d2d315bf6c9e30917ddb2d258832710e88e9","tid":284162,"uid":37822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太乾？</blockquote><br />\n唔會呀又 <br />\n係廚房成日濕水"},{"pid":"1f709de1fa3394f0cf6b93f253a2ef8444e666e1","tid":284162,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:50:30.000Z","msg":"哇咩料"},{"pid":"df2035fc1f78ba176fc015d732ee2665c7e4d73f","tid":284162,"uid":80107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:51:18.000Z","msg":"共用手套傳染香港手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12a775911103888ae0551ad2039f885745ced7f","tid"